{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u25a0CUTE and RELAXING MERGE PUZZLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drop cute foods into a hot pot, merge them, and try to get higher score until foods overflow out of the pot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914400/extras/hpg010.gif?t=1734096220\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u25a0OVER 30 UNIQUE ITEMS HELP YOU MAKE the BEST HOT POT EVER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each level increase provides you the choice of three items that help you much.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover synergies, utilize them effectively, and solve the tough situations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For example,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pencil for drawing obstacle lines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slingshot for blowing objects off</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An item for making object bigger</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Magnet that attracts objects</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hammer that enhances item effect...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914400/extras/hpg011.gif?t=1734096220\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u25a0MERGE STREAK FOR MORE ITEMS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep up a merge streak to get more exp points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As your streak gets bigger and bigger, you'll receive more and more items as rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914400/extras/hpg012.gif?t=1734096220\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u25a0FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">! Cute foods, a cozy atmosphere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">! Get exp by merging, each level provides the choice of items</p><p class=\"bb_paragr